Ragism, Tagism


2236
01:42:59.481 --> 01:43:03.569
♪ This-ism, that-ism,
is-m, is-m, is-m


2237
01:43:03.611 --> 01:43:09.117
♪ All we are saying

2238
01:43:09.158 --> 01:43:15.123
♪ Is give peace a chance

2239
01:43:15.164 --> 01:43:20.711
♪ All we are saying

2240
01:43:20.753 --> 01:43:24.590
♪ Is give peace a chance... ♪

2241
01:43:24.632 --> 01:43:28.094
He's moved further
and further away


2242
01:43:28.136 --> 01:43:29.971
from the elegant combination

2243
01:43:30.012 --> 01:43:35.017
of artistic musical
choices and resonant text


2244
01:43:35.059 --> 01:43:39.688
into records that
only have a message.


2245
01:43:39.730 --> 01:43:43.067
He had that ability to
distill something down


2246
01:43:43.109 --> 01:43:46.487
to its bare essence,
make it communicative,


2247
01:43:46.528 --> 01:43:50.032
make it unforgettable, and it
still resonates to this day.


2248
01:43:50.074 --> 01:43:52.785
[Narrator] While
Lennon pressed on


2249
01:43:52.827 --> 01:43:54.495
campaigning for peace,

2250
01:43:54.536 --> 01:43:57.248
the close of the decade saw
the first major casualties


2251
01:43:57.290 --> 01:43:58.749
of the youth movement,

2252
01:43:58.791 --> 01:44:01.127
with the death of
Rolling Stone Brian Jones


2253
01:44:01.169 --> 01:44:03.254
and permanent narcotics damage

2254
01:44:03.296 --> 01:44:06.924
on both Beach Boy Brian Wilson
