2260
01:44:21.939 --> 01:44:25.318
married his new partner Linda
Eastman in 1969,


2261
01:44:25.358 --> 01:44:28.654
none of his fellow Beatles
attended the ceremony.


2262
01:44:28.696 --> 01:44:31.573
As the world moved
into the 1970s,


2263
01:44:31.615 --> 01:44:34.076
Paul issued his
debut solo record


2264
01:44:34.118 --> 01:44:35.661
along with a press release

2265
01:44:35.703 --> 01:44:38.622
which announced that he
was quitting the band.


2266
01:44:38.664 --> 01:44:42.501
It was official.
The Beatles were no more.


2267
01:44:42.543 --> 01:44:45.420
The demise of the band
shocked their fans worldwide,


2268
01:44:45.462 --> 01:44:47.589
yet those close to the musicians

2269
01:44:47.631 --> 01:44:49.466
had watched them
gradually drift apart


2270
01:44:49.508 --> 01:44:52.261
over a two-year period.

2271
01:44:52.303 --> 01:44:54.429
There was no cohesion.

2272
01:44:54.471 --> 01:44:56.389
The old Liverpool bubble that
they all used to live in


2273
01:44:56.431 --> 01:44:59.018
and see each other all the
time and love each other


2274
01:44:59.060 --> 01:45:01.270
and be tolerant of
each other's foibles


2275
01:45:01.312 --> 01:45:02.897
and differences had gone.

2276
01:45:02.938 --> 01:45:04.899
So now they were spinning
off in different directions


2277
01:45:04.940 --> 01:45:09.653
with new ideas, new families,
