2278
01:45:09.695 --> 01:45:11.113
It just wasn't working anymore.

2279
01:45:11.155 --> 01:45:12.907
It was obvious really

2280
01:45:12.948 --> 01:45:15.617
that The Beatles as a group
had pretty much come to an end.


2281
01:45:15.659 --> 01:45:19.121
Has a multi-million
dollar entertainment act


2282
01:45:19.163 --> 01:45:24.377
ever broken up because
