2328
01:47:22.036 --> 01:47:24.830
but it's there on the table.

2329
01:47:24.872 --> 01:47:27.416
Always there on the
table, for everybody.


2330
01:47:27.458 --> 01:47:30.252
[Narrator] And as the band's
astonishing achievements


2331
01:47:30.294 --> 01:47:33.464
continue to make an impact
half a century later,


2332
01:47:33.506 --> 01:47:35.424
the legacy of The Beatles,

2333
01:47:35.466 --> 01:47:36.967
and of the remarkable decade

2334
01:47:37.009 --> 01:47:40.388
in which they flourished,
remains unrivaled.


2335
01:47:40.429 --> 01:47:43.932
The unique story of four
working class Liverpudlians


2336
01:47:43.974 --> 01:47:45.851
who changed the world.

2337
01:47:45.893 --> 01:47:47.728
[Chris] Lennon said
something along the lines of,


2338
01:47:47.769 --> 01:47:50.939
"We weren't leaders
